name: A Little Bit Of Shay D
description: UK Hip Hop: A collection of freestyles, skits and mixed content of tracks from summer vibes to honest social bars, Shay D brings you all her songs to date to a one CD which is fully mixed, scratched and arranged by DJ Shorty. Producers on the mixtape include Suspence MC and Nutty P. The original artwork is by Inuk, a graffiti artist from London. This is a authentic grassroot mixtape from this London rapper. www.shaydmusic.com

name: Once Upon A City EP
description:
Poetry flirts with Hip Hop in this six track tale of forbidden love. 

Zone out to a mixture of Trip Hop, Samples, Lounge Music and Floetry from UK rapper Shay D's debut EP.

Track Listing
1. Secrets
2. Tonight
3. Fridays Child
4. Why Did You Let Me Go
5. Sweet Love
6. The Escape
